│ Plan: Chunked Manifest-Based Resumable Upload                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                 │
│ Context                                                                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                 │
│ The current resumable upload (/fs/upload-stream-resumable) is a single-offset design:                                                           │
│ it tracks bytes written and resumes from the last byte boundary. This has no per-chunk                                                          │
│ integrity verification, no ability to skip already-good data, and no bitset tracking.                                                           │
│                                                                                                                                                 │
│ Replace it entirely with a proper chunked upload protocol:                                                                                      │
│ - Client pre-computes SHA-256 per chunk, builds a manifest                                                                                      │
│ - Server creates an upload session keyed by a random upload_id                                                                                  │
│ - Client uploads only missing chunks (any order)                                                                                                │
│ - Server validates each chunk's SHA-256 before writing                                                                                          │
│ - Server tracks completion with a binary bitset                                                                                                 │
│ - Resume: client queries which chunks arrived, uploads only the missing ones                                                                    │
